<li id="cite_note-74"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-74">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Blasphemy_law#Ireland" title="Blasphemy law">Blasphemy law#Ireland</a></span>
